{"tid":1782420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(推上熱門)教育局對官校發「禁言指引」 已FC","createTime":"2019-12-14T02:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T08:29:39.000Z","uid":285249,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"3a3dc6b258fb805641a59b3235328167207e9e9b","tid":1782420,"uid":285249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JkKr1hj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJkKr1hj.png&h=94897a54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DCyHzCk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDCyHzCk.png&h=2eececf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(已FC 麻煩推上熱門)中學校內抗爭將會被全面打壓！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782087</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n其實呢個指引都出咗一段時間 見尋日有巴打講起先醒翻起<br />\n話說我自己都讀官校 琴日發起咗和你lunch <br />\n翻到學校之後 訓導曾經話過唔會秋後算帳 結果我哋上堂嗰陣 就比校長捉咗去照肺 講咗足足3堂<br />\n其中一個副校掦言話:「<span style=\"color: red;\">唔駛上堂㗎啦 有冇得上都唔知</span>」係咪恐嚇會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">開除學藉？</span></span>有冇弦外之音？我唔知<br />\n結果我哋幾個同學要通知家長接走<br />\n雖然呢件事睇落冇乜嘢 但代表校方已經開始打壓 <br />\n希望大家記得 中學生係一條好重要嘅戰線 今日對官校發<span style=\"color: red;\">禁言指引</span> 有一日連津校 私校都唔會放過"},{"pid":"d0b5bc5e54f996c3082b2ba935eb9d9359f8d186","tid":1782420,"uid":285249,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nSdGq5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nSdGq5.png&h=ef567f4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n補返一張"},{"pid":"5ba1a40f157ee8dda40d54310f4ae312152a6c80","tid":1782420,"uid":245644,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:49:41.000Z","msg":"學生會驚咩？如識法律，大把野可以玩死學校"},{"pid":"1217a9a1650b4e4d88b67e5b30e6c80b8ad7b9c5","tid":1782420,"uid":336877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:50:41.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"9c868bfe0d1e9abbeffd66c90